      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 7.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "これが、プロのステップ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s professional dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、実際のライブバトルでは、今回と違って\n二つのグループで勝敗を競い合うことになる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. In an actual live battle‚\ntwo groups would be competing against each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.833333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ステージでの技術や能力、観客の盛り上がりが\n点数化され、勝敗はそれで決まる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’d get points based on your performance skills and abilities‚\nas well as the audience’s reaction.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "VENUSプログラムのランキングの上を目指すには\nライブバトルに勝つしかない――みんな本気だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Beating your opponents in live battles\nis the only way to climb the rankings in the VENUS Program. It’s serious business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "勝たないと、上にはいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To rise to the top‚ we have to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう。ただし、優劣を決めるのは観客だよ\n明日からみっちりレッスンしていかなきゃね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Although‚ it’s the audience who ultimately chooses the winner.\nStarting tomorrow‚ you’ll need to train hard every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さんは、わざとやらせたのだろう）\n（これから競っていくことになる存在を知らせるために）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder if Saegusa-san arranged this on purpose‚）\n（to show Kotono and Sakura what they’re up against.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……\nこれから頑張っていこうよ、一緒に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…\nLet’s give it our best. We’re in this together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……一緒に……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん\n今はまだ二人とも、力ないけど練習して成長して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nWe might not be much right now‚ but we can learn and grow stronger.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.6666666666715,
          "startTime": 76.66666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
