    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 76.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ここが、二人が暮らす寮だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the dorm where you’ll be staying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（なるべくここで過ごすことで）\n（自立心と結束を強めていくのが狙いだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The time they spend here）\n（should help their sense of independence and unity flourish.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "わあ\n普通のお家なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow!\nIt’s an actual house!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こういう方が気分も変わっていいって、三枝さんがね\n炊事洗濯掃除は、それぞれ当番制だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san thought it’d be a nice change from a typical dorm.\nYou’ll take turns doing the housework.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、料理得意？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ can you cook?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "…………ひとついいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…May I ask one question?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 99.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "どうしても……寮に入らないといけませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it necessary… that we live in the dorm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "嫌なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t want to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私、一人で出来るので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't‚ I can take care of myself alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、ダメだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope‚ not happening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "なぜですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "共同生活によって、互いのメンバーのことを理解し\nステージで活かしていくことが大切だからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Living with the other members is vital for developing a bond\nthat you can all take with you onto the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "メンバー……？\nどういうことです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Other members?\nWhat other members?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、二人には\nグループを組んでもらおうと思っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve decided\nto put you girls in an idol group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "私は、一人で出来ます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I want to go solo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "君はVENUSプログラムの頂点に\n絶対立ちたいと言った。そのためならなんでもすると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You told me your dream was to rise to the top of the VENUS Program.\nThat you would do anything to make that happen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "それが、なんなんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why is that relevant?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.33333333333334,
