    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、そのためには\nグループを結成した方がいいと思っているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I believe\nthe surest way to make that happen is for you to be part of a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんはソロでNEXT VENUSグランプリの\nステージに立ったんです、私も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But my sister made it to the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix finals on her own.\nCan’t I also—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 148.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "それでうまくいくと思う？　麻奈の妹がデビュー\n好意的に捉えられればいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think it’ll be that easy?\nThat if you’re debut solo and share Mana’s last name‚ you’ll succeed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、現実はそうとは限らないよ。売名行為だ\n七光りだと言われるかもしれない。それが、芸能界だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Reality isn’t that simple. People might think it’s just a publicity stunt.\nThat you’re just riding Mana’s coattails. That’s how this world works.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "それは、三枝さんが言ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was this Saegusa-san’s idea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_04-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "事務所の方針だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the agency’s decision.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
